    parts.append('</table>')
    parts.append('<h2>Bottom line</h2>')
    parts.append('<p>If your real risk is damage disputes at the moment someone else takes possession of your car — valet, rental return, dealer drop-off, body shop, fleet handover — CarShake is purpose-built for that exact moment. ' + comp + ' may be stronger in its own specialty, but it was not designed to win a "he said, she said" argument with a valet company over a fresh dent. That is the gap CarShake fills, and it is free to start.</p>')
