    parts.append('<h2>How to apply this</h2>')
    parts.append('<p>This guide is not theoretical. The point of understanding ' + topic.lower() + ' is to change what you actually do at the moment you hand your car to someone else. The drivers who avoid paying for damage they did not cause all follow the same four-step workflow — and the whole thing takes under 60 seconds.</p>')
