    parts.append('<li><strong>Time-stamped and geo-located photos.</strong> Are timestamps and GPS coordinates baked into the photo metadata, not just added as text overlays a user could fake?</li>')
    parts.append('<li><strong>Before/after diffing.</strong> Can it actually compare two scans and surface new damage, or does it just store photos for you to compare manually?</li>')
