def gen_faq(h1, desc, slug):
    parts = []
    parts.append('<section style="margin-top:32px">')
    parts.append('<h2>More context on this question</h2>')
    parts.append('<p>Frequently asked questions about CarShake tend to cluster around the same few concerns: is it really free, does the documentation actually hold up in disputes, how long does a scan take, and what happens when the other party denies responsibility. The short answers above cover the headline; this section gives you the deeper context that determines whether CarShake will actually work for your situation.</p>')
